title: The Honeymoon Is Over for Biden and Democrats: Susan Page and Mark Barabak
description: Afghanistan? A pandemic and misinformation campaign? A congressional showdown coming in late September? Washington Bureau Chief for USA Today Susan Page and LA Times Columnist Mark Barabak predict what's next as President Biden fight battles at home and abroad.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
